criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  to be independent according to the Katz Daily Activities Activity Scale;

          -  no problem in physical activity with the suggestion of the doctor in Family Health
             Center;

          -  living alone or with family;

          -  good cognitive state (place, time and person orientation) with the suggestion of the
             doctor; - the willingness to participate in the study

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  to live in any elderly care center or nursing home;

          -  to be semi-dependent and dependent according to the Katz Daily Activities Activity
             Scale

          -  to have a psychiatric disorder.
